Oh, I hunt for supernatural tales and oddities in my daily life,
and I run a lot. I know the secret to running longer.{短暂停}
Just run more.

In the water...{短暂停}
Having a special skill can save your life when it matters most.
That's why I learned to hold my breath first.

I understand.
Walking outdoors is also exercise. {短暂停}
Oh, you could also just lie down and do nothing instead.

...{短暂停}
Oh, that's not entirely unreasonable.
If we could make time stand still.
